---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 118
By: Buddhaghosa
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Suffering Inseparable From the
    Fallen State
  - Sacrifice-Death=Separation-Sin
---
The world is afflicted with death and decay, therefore the wise do not
grieve, knowing the terms of the world.
